Package pl.polsl.lab.bartosz.sosnica.sudoku.model

package pl.polsl.lab.bartosz.sosnica.sudoku.model
This package contains the model classes for the Sudoku game. The models represent the game state and handle the business logic.

Models:

  • BoardModel: Represents the Sudoku board and its state.
  • GameModel: Manages the overall game state and logic.
  • UserModel: Manages user-related data and preferences.
